name: Quantum Strike (V2)
description: "Quantum Strike" is a set of 3 hard, colourful Boom-format maps designed to be played from a Pistol Start. Gameplay is purely action-based with simple progression and generally high monster density. UV is meant to challenge "good at Doom" individuals and masochists who don't mind dying repeatedly. HMP should be more fun/reasonable and HNTR more laid back.
